title: Neff Skate Team Teaser
description: Neff is excited to welcome new pros Leo Romero, Silas Baxter-Neal, Matt Bennett, Aaron "jaws" Homoki, Dakota Servold, and Derrick Wilson. They will be joining Nick Trapasso, Moose, Ryan Decenzo and Nick Merlino. "We are very excited to add these amazing skaters to our team. Stay tuned for lots of content coming very soon." - Chip Neff
